The OCR Workflow app enables the processing of various files using OCR algorithms. The processing is facilitated through the workflow engine, allowing easy customization according to specific requirements.

It's important to note that in order to process PDF files, you'll need to install the OcrMyPDF Command-Line Interface  on your Nextcloud server. You can find detailed installation instructions in the documentation, which can be accessed at https://github.com/R0Wi/workflow_ocr/blob/master/README.md. Make sure to follow the provided instructions to set up the necessary components for seamless OCR processing of PDF documents within Nextcloud.
